title: RADWOOD's Art and Layne!
description:
RADWOOD is arguably the greatest car show of our time and Art and Lane are two of the founding members of the event. RADWOOD features cars from the 80s and 90s, but it's more than that. It's a costume show, there's music from the 80s and 90s, old school skateboarding, and a sense of humor about it. It's growing every year, internationally. If you haven't been, go. 

https://www.radwood.co/

T: @thesmokingtire, @zackklapman

IG: @thesmokingtire, @fakezackklapman @art.sees @laneskelton

 

Watch the show: https://youtu.be/yxR_zcvpmHs
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
